name: Labyrinth - Labyrinth Pro
description:
Do you like classic maze games where you control the ball by tilting the maze?

Do you like to challenge yourself?

Labyrinth Pro is an awesome maze maze game with 64 well designed levels, smooth gameplay and stunning graphics!

Play and share your results with your friends!

characteristics:

  • Variety of levels, from easy to insane.

  • Realistic physics.

  • Beautiful 3D balls.

  • Sound effects.

  • Calibration.
